  "texts": [
    "First, researchers fine-tuned ChatGPT using a pre-trained model with specific questions and human-labeled answers.",
    "They would collect a large number of high-quality responses that are consistent with human values through crowdsourcing, then conduct supervised training on ChatGPT to align the model's responses with labeled ones.",
    "The first stage of RLHF resembles the role of intelligence in Dewey's habit reconstruction.",
    "Artificial labeling serves as value selection, while supervised learning is analogous to normative training.",
    "Both value selection and normative training resemble human intelligence and result from rational and proactive participation."
  ],
